H0.text: Who did Jack Ruby shoot in November 1963. Lee Harvey Oswald's brother

H1.text: Who did Jack Ruby shoot in November 1963. A police officer

H2.text: Who did Jack Ruby shoot in November 1963. A government official

H3.text: Who did Jack Ruby shoot in November 1963. L.H.O

A4.text: Jack Ruby shot Lee Harvey Oswald on Sunday, November 24, at 11:21 a.m., as Oswald was being escorted to a car in the basement of Dallas Police headquarters.

A5.text: Ruby was convicted of Oswald's murder, though the decision was overturned on appeal.
